Class Dialect

java.lang.Object
  com.mysema.query.grammar.Dialect

public class Dialect
extends java.lang.Object

Dialect provides different SQL dialects for querydsl-sql. Querydsl SQL supports the following database systems :

  • HSQLDB
  • MySQL
  • Oracle
  • PostgreSQL
  • SQL Server
